query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(t mc) NoMergeJoin(mc t ct) NoMergeJoin(ct mc mi t it) */ select min(t.title) AS american_movie
from title AS t
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2012 AND mc.note not like '%(TV)%' AND mc.note like '%(USA)%'
inner join company_type AS ct
on ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('English',
'American',
'Danish',
'German',
'Sweden',
'Denmark',
'Norway',
'America',
'USA',
'Germany')
inner join info_type AS it
on it.id = mi.info_type_id;
